<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:25:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于欧洲和中国需求稳定，Ralph Lauren 收入增长 1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-posts-rise-quarterly-revenue-2024-08-07/</link><description>拉尔夫·劳伦公司 (Ralph Lauren Corp) 周三公布季度收入增长，受益于欧洲和亚洲对其昂贵牛仔布和 Polo 衫的稳定需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:08:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-posts-rise-quarterly-revenue-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大前间谍机构负责人维涅奥特加入美国情报公司Strider</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/former-canadian-spy-agency-chief-vigneault-joins-us-intelligence-firm-strider-2024-08-07/</link><description>加拿大前间谍机构负责人戴维·维尼奥特 (David Vigneault) 在担任该职位七年后于 7 月辞职，该公司周三表示，他将加入美国安全公司 Strider Technologies，担任其全球情报部门的董事总经理。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/former-canadian-spy-agency-chief-vigneault-joins-us-intelligence-firm-strider-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行缓解市场偏头痛和超微疼痛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-07/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:09:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>西门子能源首席执行官呼吁亚洲风电公司进入欧洲进行公平竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>西门子能源首席执行官周三表示，活跃在欧洲的中国和西方风力涡轮机制造商必须在相同的市场条件下销售产品，以创造公平竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者在中国针对恒大集团提出清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿书，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者称恒大集团在中国提交清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-says-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>据请愿者周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-says-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国6月出口降幅超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-forecast-june-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三官方数据显示，由于该国主要贸易伙伴美国和欧盟其他国家的需求疲软，德国六月份出口降幅超出预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-forecast-june-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>彪马因货运成本高、中国市场低迷而缩小了财年利润前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</link><description>德国运动服装制造商彪马周三缩小了全年核心利润预期，导致其股价短暂跌至 2018 年低点，理由是货运成本上升、汇率不利以及中国消费者信心持续低迷。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>拜尔斯道夫未达到利润预期，称中国经济放缓影响了奢侈品牌销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nivea-maker-beiersdorfs-sales-grow-despite-china-weakness-2024-08-07/</link><description>妮维雅 (Nivea) 制造商拜尔斯道夫 (Beiersdorf) 周三的半年营业利润未达预期，并表示中国奢侈品市场放缓影响了其莱珀妮 (La Prairie) 品牌的销售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nivea-maker-beiersdorfs-sales-grow-despite-china-weakness-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海黄岩岛附近举行联合作战巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>南部战区在微信应用程序上发帖称，中国军队周三在南海黄岩岛附近组织海空联合作战巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行拯救了局面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>Stella Qiu 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡星展银行上调 2024 年预期，因强劲的财富流动推动利润增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</link><description>新加坡最大的银行星展集团受益于蓬勃发展的财富业务，将资产和费用收入推至创纪录水平，周三，星展集团上调了全年利润指引。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国进口恢复增长但出口放缓引发前景担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</link><description>7月份，中国的出口增长速度为三个月来最慢，低于预期，加剧了人们对庞大制造业前景的担忧，而在美国预期的科技限制措施之前急于增加芯片供应，导致进口增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:52:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国终止多国海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>菲律宾周三表示，三艘中国海军舰艇尾随菲律宾与加拿大、美国和澳大利亚在有争议的南海海域举行的联合军事演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大清算人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，陷入困境的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的清算人已对普华永道采取法律行动，指责其在为集团工作时“疏忽”和“失实陈述”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>